Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.61,0:01:35.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:93615,95491}Meimi Haneoka is 14 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.65,0:01:39.20,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:95658,99203}By day she is a happy student\Nat St. Paulia School.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.95,0:01:42.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:99954,102373}But at night, she becomes\Nthe thief St. Tail…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.41,0:01:44.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:102415,104834}to do good deeds for all who\Ncome asking the help of Seira…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.87,0:01:46.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:104876,106669}a nun in training.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.79,0:01:52.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:107795,112050}Looking to capture the elusive\NSt. Tail is an amateur detective…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.09,0:01:54.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:112091,114093}and Meimi's classmate, Asuka Jr.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.92,0:01:56.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:114927,116679}As for Meimi…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.72,0:01:59.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:116721,119724}she may have more than a bit of\Ninterest in such a determined boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.89,0:02:06.23,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:121893,126230}Legend of Happiness?\NThe Clock Tower Commotion
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.28,0:02:19.16,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:136282,139160}Did you see the ad\Nfor the Wonder Garden?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.20,0:02:21.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:139202,141371}It just opened this month.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.70,0:02:24.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:141704,144082}Oh, I love amusement parks!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.29,0:02:26.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:144290,146709}Actually, I've already been there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.79,0:02:29.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:147794,149170}Who with?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.75,0:02:32.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:150755,152006}If you must know…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.34,0:02:36.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:154342,156761}Look, it's Tominaga from class C!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.01,0:02:38.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:157011,158137}Since when?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.97,0:02:42.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:158971,162850}It's a wonderful place.\NThe flowers are really lovely.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.93,0:02:45.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:162934,165687}But the main attraction is… this!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.10,0:02:49.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:167105,169357}The mechanical clock\Nof Wonder Castle!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.44,0:02:51.40,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:169440,171401}The dolls move and it's so beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.11,0:02:55.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:172110,175363}It was built by a famous\Nforeign doll-maker.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.61,0:02:59.20,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:175613,179200}Every one of his creations\Ncosts a huge amount of money.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.82,0:03:01.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:179826,181786}Also, it's said that if…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.86,0:03:06.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:181869,186290}you watch this clock with the one\Nyou love, it'll bring happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.33,0:03:07.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:186332,187959}And you watched it together!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.41,0:03:09.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:188418,189252}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.75,0:03:11.21,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:189752,191212}How wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.62,0:03:15.34,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:191629,195341}I'm jealous, I've never\Neven been on a date.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.80,0:03:18.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:195800,198094}Who do you want to date, Meimi?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.17,0:03:21.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:198177,201597}Don't tell me\Nyou want to date Asuka Jr.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.09,0:03:23.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:202098,203433}Don't be silly!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.76,0:03:26.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:203766,206269}Who'd want to date\Na dinky detective like him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.60,0:03:28.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:206602,208187}Just who do you think\Nyou're calling "dinky"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.27,0:03:29.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:208271,209897}If that bugs you,\Nwhy don't you go ahead…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.93,0:03:31.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:209939,211607}and catch St. Tail,\Nyou bungling detective!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.69,0:03:34.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:211691,214652}Even if I do capture her,\NI'm not letting you see her!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.69,0:03:36.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:214694,216863}Who cares, she's not like\Nsome beetle on display, is she?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.90,0:03:37.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:216904,217739}Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.82,0:03:38.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:217822,218990}Same to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.11,0:03:41.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:220116,221617}Hey, Asuka!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.07,0:03:43.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:222076,223828}Yeah, I'm coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.91,0:03:48.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:227915,228833}Seira…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.42,0:03:54.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:233421,234630}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.67,0:03:57.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:234672,237717}Meimi, there's only one reason\Nwhy I would ask you to come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.67,0:04:01.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:238676,241304}I have a favor to ask of St. Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.88,0:04:03.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:241888,243806}Something that only she can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.59,0:04:06.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:244599,246058}The doll at the amusement park?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.14,0:04:08.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:246142,248436}Yes, and it's located\Nin a very high place.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.72,0:04:10.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:248728,250438}You mean that amusement park?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.68,0:04:13.23,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:250688,253232}Yes, Wonder Garden\NAmusement Park.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.31,0:04:15.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:253316,255276}Then, by a high place,\Nyou must mean…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.35,0:04:17.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:255359,257862}The mechanical clock\Nof Wonder Castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.69,0:04:21.74,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:258696,261741}This girl tied a precious doll\Nthat she had brought with her…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.78,0:04:23.74,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:261783,263743}to the strings of her balloons.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.95,0:04:25.57,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:263951,265578}This is the doll you\Nwant me to get?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.87,0:04:29.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:265870,269248}Yes, she borrowed the doll\Nfrom a friend…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.29,0:04:31.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:269290,271709}and must return it\Nthe next time they meet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.66,0:04:33.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:272668,273920}However…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.55,0:04:50.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:288559,290186}The doll!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.12,0:05:14.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:312124,314544}They contacted the\Namusement park…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.79,0:05:18.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:314794,318756}but were told to forget\Nabout the doll.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.34,0:05:21.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:319340,321509}All I have to do is\Nget the doll back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.80,0:05:23.21,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:321801,323219}That's easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.26,0:05:25.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:323261,325263}Only, you have to get\Nit back by Sunday.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.42,0:05:27.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:325429,327974}Sunday… that's tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.51,0:05:33.39,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:328516,333396}The doll's owner is coming to the\Ngirl's house tomorrow to play.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.52,0:05:34.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:333521,334522}She needs it by then.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.56,0:05:36.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:334564,336274}Which means I have\Nto do it tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.35,0:05:39.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:336357,339902}And the doll emerges from\Nthe clock on the hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.77,0:05:43.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:340778,343739}So you have to get the doll\Nbefore the balloon carries it away.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.90,0:05:45.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:343906,345908}Okay, leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.41,0:05:50.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:349412,350538}I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.33,0:05:52.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:351330,352665}Welcome back, Meimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.33,0:05:54.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:353332,354709}What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.83,0:05:55.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:354834,355626}This…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.04,0:05:57.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:356043,357795}You haven't gone\Nthere yet, have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.83,0:05:59.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:357837,359714}Huh…? No.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.08,0:06:04.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:360089,364552}We were just about to go.\NDo you want to come, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.17,0:06:09.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:367179,369849}It'll complicate things\Nif I go with them…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.26,0:06:12.31,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:370266,372310}You want to go, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.47,0:06:13.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:372476,373477}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.72,0:06:14.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:373728,374979}Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.06,0:06:18.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:375062,378733}Besides, you might find\Nsome ideas for new magic tricks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.27,0:06:22.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:380276,382778}Jeez, they always use\Nme as an excuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.07,0:06:29.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:388075,389619}You want to come?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.45,0:06:32.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:390453,392788}But I've got work to do…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.62,0:06:35.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:393623,395374}Ready yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.62,0:06:37.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:395625,397043}Almost.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.00,0:06:40.21,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:398002,400212}I want you to stay home\Nand watch the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.22,0:06:52.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:410222,412725}It's been a long time since I've\Nbeen to an amusement park.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.93,0:06:55.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:413935,415978}It's time for the doll to come out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.89,0:06:59.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:416896,419148}Hey, hey… what's the rush?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.06,0:07:02.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:420066,422068}I have something I want to see!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.65,0:07:09.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:428658,429867}There.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.03,0:07:11.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:430034,431535}It's almost time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.66,0:07:16.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:435665,436832}Asuka Jr.!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.87,0:07:17.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:436874,437959}Haneoka!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.00,0:07:20.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:438000,440378}What brings you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.41,0:07:23.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:440419,443673}To have fun… what else?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.04,0:07:26.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:444048,446634}Yeah, that makes sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.96,0:07:30.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:446968,450096}So that's the clock tower\Nthe girls were fussing over?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.35,0:07:37.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:455351,457144}When you watch it with\Nthe one you love…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.18,0:07:38.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:457186,458521}it brings happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.94,0:07:45.11,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:462942,465111}Why don't they come out?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.11,0:07:48.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:466112,468531}Hey there, what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.61,0:07:50.32,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:468614,470324}Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.36,0:07:52.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:470366,472284}It's just some malfunction.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.32,0:07:55.20,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:472326,475204}There's a temp repairman here,\Nif I remember correctly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.24,0:07:56.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:475246,476872}Yes, I'll get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.70,0:08:00.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:478708,480543}They say it's just\Nsome malfunction.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.58,0:08:01.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:480584,481711}See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.88,0:08:06.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:484880,486966}Ah! …My balloon!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.13,0:08:09.34,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:488134,489343}That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.38,0:08:11.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:489385,491595}At least I can check\Nif the balloons are still there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.80,0:08:13.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:491804,493723}Too bad, Meimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.88,0:08:17.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:493889,497727}I'm going to go get some ice cream.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.52,0:08:23.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:499520,503107}"Employees Only"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.49,0:08:34.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:511490,514076}Oh, it's a costume.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.41,0:08:42.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:520416,522752}Good, it's still there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.25,0:08:49.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:528257,529633}Good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.30,0:08:52.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:530301,532762}All I did was remove a gear.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.80,0:08:54.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:532803,534138}Piece of cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.18,0:08:56.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:534180,536432}The big job's coming up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.51,0:09:01.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:539518,541020}Identical dolls.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.10,0:09:03.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:541103,543147}Why bother with all this stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.18,0:09:05.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:543189,545483}Why not just go ahead and steal it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.64,0:09:07.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:545649,547777}The police are on guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.86,0:09:09.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:547860,549945}Sometimes it's better\Nto use your brain.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.69,0:09:11.98,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:550696,551989}Well, faking a malfunction…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.03,0:09:14.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:552031,554241}and switching the dolls\Nduring the repair…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.28,0:09:15.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:554283,555493}I guess that's using your brain.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.78,0:09:17.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:555785,557787}Which means those are all fakes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.12,0:09:20.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:559121,560623}Who's there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.87,0:09:26.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:563876,566295}Cool it! It's nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.54,0:09:29.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:566545,569090}Okay, let's get to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.01,0:09:39.39,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:578015,579391}They won't\Nget away with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.10,0:09:44.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:583104,584355}Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.44,0:09:49.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:587441,589610}Please come by.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.19,0:09:57.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:595199,597910}It's an ad for Wonder Garden.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.16,0:10:04.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:599161,604333}"I'm going to Wonder Garden\Ntonight to get the doll… St. Tail."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.37,0:10:05.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:604375,605417}How dare she!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.45,0:10:06.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:605459,606836}She was in that\Nrabbit costume!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.17,0:10:16.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:614176,616303}I'll return this later.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.47,0:10:17.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:616470,617763}Haneoka!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.43,0:10:21.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:620432,621642}What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.68,0:10:23.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:621684,623352}That amusement park…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.97,0:10:27.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:624979,627106}That clock at Wonder Castle\Nwith the dolls that's said to…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.81,0:10:30.23,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:628816,630234}You mean…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.60,0:10:34.57,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:630609,634572}bring happiness to couples when\Nthey view it together.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.65,0:10:35.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:634655,635781}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.82,0:10:38.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:635823,638617}Is he trying to ask\Nme to go with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.82,0:10:41.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:639827,641495}About how much is it worth?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.95,0:10:43.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:641954,643622}Excuse me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.03,0:10:46.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:644039,646584}Is it true that it's very expensive?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.75,0:10:48.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:646750,648919}It's supposed to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.17,0:10:53.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:649170,653007}Why would she do\Nsomething so villainous?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.59,0:10:57.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:655593,657678}I got it, never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.92,0:10:58.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:657928,658929}See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.93,0:11:03.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:661932,663934}What's with him, anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.47,0:11:05.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:664476,665978}I hate him!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.32,0:11:24.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:682328,684455}He's so insensitive.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.99,0:11:27.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:684997,687333}Oh, look who's grouchy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.46,0:11:32.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:689460,692087}I'll take you the next time I go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.92,0:11:35.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:693923,695799}I've got to get to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.92,0:11:38.34,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:696926,698344}Meimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.43,0:11:45.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:704433,705643}Meimi?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.68,0:11:46.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:705684,706936}Are you there?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.51,0:11:48.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:707519,708604}Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.06,0:11:50.31,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:709063,710314}What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.39,0:11:51.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:710397,711941}She's not answering.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.90,0:11:58.57,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:715903,718572}What are you doing over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.49,0:12:03.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:721492,723994}I was thinking of going to\Nget some juice or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.74,0:12:05.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:724745,725913}From the window?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.99,0:12:07.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:725996,727957}I thought I'd try something new.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.04,0:12:10.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:729041,730709}I'll be off, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.12,0:12:15.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:732127,735089}Going in and out\Nof the window at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.58,0:12:17.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:735589,737883}She's my girl, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.27,0:12:38.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:755276,758946}Please forgive me,\Nfor I use no gimmick or trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.24,0:12:45.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:764243,765369}One!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.24,0:12:48.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:767246,768330}Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.83,0:12:52.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:770833,772501}Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.10,0:13:11.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:788100,791895}May the blessings\Nof God be with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.08,0:13:35.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:811081,815127}That doll was specially made.\NIt's invaluable…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.16,0:13:37.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:815169,817921}There's only one of its\Nkind in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.96,0:13:39.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:817963,819923}If it were ever stolen…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.21,0:13:41.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:820215,821633}Please be rest assured…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.96,0:13:45.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:821967,825137}St. Tail always has some\Nreason for stealing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.38,0:13:46.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:825387,826638}I'm sure it's the same this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.68,0:13:48.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:826680,828265}You can't be too sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.30,0:13:49.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:828307,829141}Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.18,0:13:53.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:829183,833979}If the latest artwork thefts\Nare the work of St. Tail…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.31,0:13:56.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:834313,836565}then everything falls into place.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.94,0:13:58.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:836940,838650}No, it can't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.77,0:14:00.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:838776,840444}You're still green, son.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.48,0:14:03.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:840486,843447}She may be called "Saint", but\Nshe's no more than a thief.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.82,0:14:07.32,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:844823,847326}I'm done with the repairs for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.74,0:14:08.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:847743,848994}All right, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.03,0:14:10.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:849036,850037}Don't mention it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.57,0:14:11.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:850579,851580}What an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.95,0:14:14.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:851955,854041}If St. Tail is going to appear…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.50,0:14:17.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:854500,857252}it'll be when the dolls come out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.79,0:14:20.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:859797,860881}What the…?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.89,0:14:38.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:875896,878774}"These dolls are fake!\NSt. Tail"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.19,0:14:40.23,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:879191,880234}St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.56,0:14:41.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:880567,881819}When did she…?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.23,0:14:44.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:882236,884738}Don't tell me she\Nswitched them with fakes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.53,0:14:47.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:886532,887950}St. Tail! Where is she?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.03,0:14:49.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:888033,889993}Stay calm, don't leave your posts!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.66,0:14:54.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:891662,894581}They still don't get it?\NTalk about dense.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.54,0:15:01.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:900546,901839}I won't let you get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.55,0:15:07.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:905551,907719}She's trying to confuse us\Nwith bits of paper!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.30,0:15:10.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:908303,910222}I can see right through you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.55,0:15:12.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:910556,912307}Light her face up! Her face!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.55,0:15:16.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:913559,916937}I can see right through you, too!\NIf you want to light up something…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.10,0:15:18.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:917104,918897}leave it to St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.06,0:15:22.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:920065,922860}It's Show Time!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.90,0:15:26.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:924903,926738}The lights are moving by themselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.13,0:15:48.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:947134,948427}What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.63,0:15:51.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:948635,951180}We don't light up at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.47,0:15:52.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:951472,952890}Now for the real show.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.89,0:16:01.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:959897,961648}Hold it! St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.28,0:16:16.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:975287,976413}I can't see!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.60,0:16:40.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:999603,1000979}Identical dolls.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.10,0:16:42.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1002105,1002940}These!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.02,0:16:44.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1003023,1004274}These are the real ones!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.35,0:16:46.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1004358,1006944}And there's the statue\Nthat was stolen last week.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.90,0:16:48.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1007903,1008946}Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.28,0:16:54.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1013283,1014826}You're under arrest!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.66,0:17:02.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1020666,1022334}Ouch, you're squashing me, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.43,0:17:19.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1038433,1039518}St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.06,0:17:28.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1046066,1048068}The rest of you, go after St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.28,0:17:33.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1052281,1053532}Here goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.61,0:17:34.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1053615,1054283}One…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.49,0:17:35.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1054491,1055367}Two…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.49,0:17:36.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1055492,1056785}Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.95,0:17:43.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1062958,1063917}Asuka Jr!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.16,0:17:45.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1064167,1065752}Which one should we arrest?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.16,0:17:47.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1066169,1067629}Yikes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.75,0:17:51.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1069756,1071258}What the…?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.30,0:17:54.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1071300,1074386}Do you have a St. Tail parade\Nor something at this amusement park?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.46,0:17:56.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1074469,1076263}Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.14,0:18:04.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1083145,1084605}I lost her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.64,0:18:10.31,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1086648,1090319}Fantastic, isn't it?\NSt. Tail's illusion parade!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.11,0:18:15.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1091111,1095616}There's no way to\Nfind me in all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.71,0:18:35.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1114718,1115719}No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.26,0:18:37.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1116261,1117304}Don't underestimate me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.38,0:18:39.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1117387,1119973}No matter where you go…\NI'll find you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.55,0:18:41.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1120557,1121725}How?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.18,0:18:45.39,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1124186,1125395}You're not getting away!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.56,0:18:49.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1127564,1129858}Asuka Jr.! That's dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.82,0:18:57.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1136823,1137949}Fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.03,0:18:59.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1138033,1139284}I won't…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.28,0:19:01.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1140285,1141953}miss this chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.83,0:19:10.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1147834,1150295}Like I said… I'm taking\Nthe doll with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.50,0:19:11.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1150504,1151797}The doll…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.83,0:19:15.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1152839,1155050}That's the doll\Nyou wanted?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.59,0:19:19.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1155592,1159304}If you had asked me out,\Nit would've made me happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.80,0:19:21.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1160806,1161682}But…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.93,0:19:24.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1162933,1164476}it turned out to be\Nlike a date, anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.55,0:19:26.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1164559,1166061}I really enjoyed myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.85,0:19:27.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1166853,1167854}Date…?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.02,0:19:30.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1169022,1170482}Cut the jokes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.94,0:19:37.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1175946,1177864}I'm serious, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.87,0:19:50.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1186873,1190001}I'm serious… darn.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.29,0:19:54.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1192295,1194464}Thank you, Asuka Jr.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.84,0:19:59.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1194840,1199261}All of the dolls have been recovered,\Nthanks to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.42,0:20:04.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1199428,1204266}Those two turned out to be the ones\Nresponsible for the art thefts.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.93,0:20:08.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1204933,1208437}I thought it was strange\Nfor her to do such a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.60,0:20:09.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1208603,1209229}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.47,0:20:11.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1209479,1211523}No, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.78,0:20:27.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1224786,1227372}Don't ever tie it to\Na balloon again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.17,0:20:41.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1238175,1241178}It brings happiness if you watch it\Ntogether with the one you love.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.59,0:20:43.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1241595,1243180}Well, who cares…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.38,0:20:48.39,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1243388,1248393}My nights are always filled\Nwith the prospect of happiness.
